      "title": "SC issues travel ban on Mahinda and Basil",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Supreme Court today (July 15) issued a travel ban on former Prime Minister Mahinda Rajapaksa and former Finance Minister Basil Rajapaksa.",
        "Accordingly, the two brothers are barred from flying out of the country until the 28th of July."
      ],
